Hazell's Social & Sport Club Ground, Aylesbury, Buckinghamshire, England, UK Contest open to bands which had not won a cash prize exceeding £8 since January 1928. 1st place awarded The 'Boosey' Challenge Sheild and £7 cash 2nd place awarded the 'British Bandsman' Challenge Cup and £4 cash Mr W Wright (Chesham Silver Band) won a medal for best Euphonium playing. 2 bands competed
